        "spreadNumber": 3
      },
      {
        "text": "Suddenly, a tiny squirrel with a large, bushy tail popped out from behind a tree. It was Squeaky! Squeaky chattered excitedly, pointing a tiny paw towards the briar patch. Squeaky seemed to be warning ╪│╪º╪▒╪⌐, bouncing with energy, clearly ready to help. ╪│╪º╪▒╪⌐ watched, confused, as Squeaky continued to chatter and point towards the briar patch.",
        "spreadNumber": 4
      },
      {
        "text": "Then, an amazing thing happened. ╪│╪º╪▒╪⌐ understood what Squeaky was saying! Squeaky chattered that the briar patch protected the Elder Tree, a place of great wisdom. But Squeaky warned that the briar patch was also home to grumpy, sleepy insects that would sting if woken. ╪│╪º╪▒╪⌐'s shoulders slumped. Disappointment flooded in. The Elder Tree sounded wonderful, but no one wanted to get stung!",
        "spreadNumber": 5
      },
      {
        "text": "╪│╪º╪▒╪⌐ sat, dejected, then a new thought sparked. If Squeaky could be understood, what if listening even closer to everything around worked? Maybe the insects could be understood too! Closing their eyes, ╪│╪º╪▒╪⌐ focused. Feeling the forest floor beneath their hands, ╪│╪º╪▒╪⌐ asked the forest for a quiet way to pass and asked the Elder Tree for advice. An idea began to form...",
        "spreadNumber": 6
      },
      {
        "text": "Taking a deep breath, ╪│╪º╪▒╪⌐ approached the briar patch, this time with a new plan. A soft, gentle voice spoke to the insects, offering a quiet song, a peaceful melody just for them. Slowly and carefully, the insects stirred. The thorny branches shifted aside, making a small path. With the path clear, ╪│╪º╪▒╪⌐ stepped carefully through the briar patch, deeper into the woods.",
